      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"hope\" stuff feels so scripted though. Like, you don't get it. It's not just being sad, it's just... the math of it. I'm halfway across the world, no one here knows my name, and my family doesn't even know what time it is for me. If I just wasn't here tomorrow, the only thing that would change is a tiny bit of space in a cafe or a room. It's like I'm already gone, just waiting for my body to catch up.",
